snippet.title: Interstellar Orphan: Early Preview
snippet.description:
Working on this sandbox RPG of a rogue planet looking for a star system to call home. Releasing a demo soon, since it's for a weekly game jam:
https://itch.io/jam/weekly-game-jam-129

Visit fey.earth or our Itch.io page to learn more about our games:
https://kourtnie.itch.io/
